    "These legal restrictions have impacted where and when smoking is acceptable. 4.",
    "**Gender Roles**: In some historical contexts, gender roles might have played a role in shaping smoking etiquette.",
    "However, modern texts tend to focus more on general guidelines for all individuals, irrespective of gender. 5.",
    "**Health Concerns**: The increasing awareness of the health hazards of smoking has led to changes in smoking behavior and etiquette.",
